Subject: re: [Q] Westy Rear-Facing Seat

If you mean the rear facing jump seats, they should come with their
own lap belts.  I installed a pair from a Vanagon in our '72 Bus.
Required a bit of welding for the brackets, but they pop in and out
and the seat bottoms flip up for more room.

Dave
